Business Brief -- West Co.:
   Marketing, Technology Pact
   Is Signed With Two Firms
The technology exchange agreements allow for the licensing
of several Daikyo products, including a pharmaceutical
stopper coating, a rubber formulation and a stopper surface
treatment, by West and Pharma-Gummi. Conversely, a number of
West and Pharma-Gummi products, such as an advanced closure
system, medical grade tubing, and pharmaceutical glass
products, will be sold in Japan.